m4 Directory Reference

Files

file  ammu.h
 This file contains the interfaces present in the AMMU HAL. This also contains some related macros, structures and enums.
 
file  m4/interrupt.h
 This file contains the API prototypes for configuring INTC for ARM Cortex-M4.
 
file  ipu_ecc.h
 This file contains the API prototypes for configuring ECC for ARM Cortex-M4.
 
file  ipu_wugen.h
 This file contains the API prototypes for configuring MPU_WUGEN for ARM Cortex-M4.
 
file  unicache.h
 This file contains the interfaces present in the Uni-cache HAL. This also contains some related macros, structures and enums.
